afterSignInUrl.description: Full URL or path to navigate after successful sign in.

afterSignUpUrl.description: Full URL or path to navigate after successful sign up.
afterSignUpUrl.name: afterSignUpUrl

redirectUrl.description:
Full URL or path to navigate after successful sign in
or sign up.

The same as setting afterSignInUrl and afterSignUpUrl
to the same value.
redirectUrl.name: redirectUrl

secondFactorUrl.description:
Full URL or path to navigate during sign in,
if 2FA is enabled.
secondFactorUrl.name: secondFactorUrl

continueSignUpUrl.description: Full URL or path to navigate after an incomplete sign up.
continueSignUpUrl.name: continueSignUpUrl
